This paper focuses on optimization algorithms in memetic computing, which is a subfield of computational intelligence. The paper proposes a simple algorithmic approach and presents experimental results on various test problems and a digital signal processing application. Based on this information, the most likely sub-category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
